# My Awesome Project

This is a sample README to demonstrate DialectOS translation.

## Features

- Fast and reliable
- Supports multiple platforms
- Easy to use

## Installation

```bash
npm install my-awesome-project
```

## API Reference

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/users` | GET | List all users |
| `/users` | POST | Create a new user |

